<div class="wrapper">

	<article class="stack">
		<header class="page-header">
			<h1>Hello</h1>
		</header>

		<p>My name is Matt and I make websites. That means I talk to people to understand their goals, their users' needs and thinking. I plan ongoing digital and content strategies. I work with designers to integrate brands into digital experiences and products. I also do a bit of coding.</p>

		<p>I work for the <a href="//bluegg.co.uk">best design agency in Wales</a>.</p>

		<p>Here is some writing:</p>

		{% set posts = collections.blog | reverse  %}

		{% for post in posts %}
		{% if loop.index0 < 5 %}
		<article class="snippet border">
			<h2>
				<a href="{{ post.url | url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
			</h2>
			<time datetime="{{ post.date | dateIso }}">{{ post.date | dateReadable }}</time>
			<p>{{ post.data.snippet }}</p>
		</article>
		{% endif %}
		{% endfor %}

		<p><a href="/blog">More writing</a></p>
		
	</article>

</div>
